This paper deals with parameter estimation for mixture models and hidden Markov models, which are commonly used in machine learning and statistics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IT (Information Theory) as these sub-categories are also related to machine learning and statistical modeling. Additionally, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.ST (Statistics) are also possible sub-categories as they deal with statistical modeling and algorithms.
